{
  "stem": "10588.11",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even before Germany came in, there was already a  new cemetery, which was much farther from here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here in the back there were houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My girlfriend used to live here and other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very populated, Jewish community and now this happened-- no graves, no tombstones, no markers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You vanished all in agony, smoke, and flames, bereft and broken-hearted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On my soul, I engraved their names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't forget you, dear sisters and brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember your anguish and cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Six million innocent men, women, and little children, oh God, who did not want to die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am very disturbed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as I arrived here, I found a woman who lives in Poland and was extremely kind to me, even offered to show me around.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this-- in contrast to this kind woman that I just met, never knew, and shows a lot of kindness to me-- I'm coming to the place where my grandmother and other relatives have been buried at this cemetery.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found that even though there are no Jews, I still see a swastika.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there it says, 'Jude raus.' And this was what the Nazis said to me, when they came in the middle of the night to chase us out from Ciechanow, Poland on October 15th, 1941, and put us to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here I see a slogan, which I heard before the Nazis chased me out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the slogan said in Polish, [POLISH], which means the houses are yours, but the streets are ours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, and here it says, [POLISH], Poland is yours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't come here to take away Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I came here to remember the wonderful times I had here as a child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And frankly, when I see this here, they can keep Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They can keep Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't come to take away anything, only to revive memories and to share them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I am a witness to the darkest chapter of human history.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If people can still do this, and other people didn't even bother to erase it or to do something, I'm deeply disappointed and hurt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this is the square.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It used to be called the market, in Yiddish, the [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here was the most contact that the Jewish people had with the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Jewish people-- like shoemakers, and tailors, and other craftsmen-- would bring their merchandise, what they made by hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people from the small villages around would bring livestock and would bring things that  were growing-- vegetables and fruit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it used to be so busy, twice a week, and so colorful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that we used to come here-- and just to point out the changes, now, when we are in America, we always look to eat food that is not fat.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Polish, when we used to buy from the peasants a chicken, we used to blow on the back of the chicken to see if it's yellow, if it's a lot of fat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To take the relationships between non-Jewish people-- Polish-- and the Jewish people that had most of the relationships here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to exchange what they brought to sell and what they brought able to sell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was  a warm friendship in this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people came here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And usually the Jewish people came her to buy for the Sabbat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They bought all the things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not only the food was different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember something now, when I think--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember this square, because I used to come here sometimes twice a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because twice a week, they had the market here, where the peasants from the small villages would bring livestock, vegetables, and fruit that they grew to sell.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other hand, the Jewish people who made-- shoemakers brought their shoes, their boots, tailors bought their clothes, and other merchants whatever they brought, and they used to exchange.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to always get a kick out of when sometimes they would barter, he said, I'll pay you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, how much do you want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would say so many zloty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would say, I give you so much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And may I see you for a moment please?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would deal like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK, I give you 5 zloty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, I give you 4 zloty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he said, OK, let's make it 3 zloty, shake.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they shook.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was-- I remember as a child seeing this here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what I also remember, the difference in our perception of what good food is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we used to buy livestock-- chickens, ducks, geese, or turkeys-- they used to blow at the back of the chicken, to see if it's fat.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
